## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the scope of the search. The analysis primarily focuses on Western feminism, which may not fully represent global feminist movements. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of digital activism means that some recent developments may not be fully captured. Further research could explore non-Western perspectives and the impact of emerging technologies on feminist activism.